snippet.title: Sonic Boll 1.9.2 :: First Look Gameplay (720p/60fps)
snippet.description:
The return of Sonic Boll! Originally, I did have gameplay on the first 1.9 until noticing a 1.9.2, which there are some slight differences. Anyways, lots of progress has happened during the time of 1.8, new main menu, new slot of characters (including 2 locked ones), not a lot of character skins like Boll Classic use to have, but this is still cool though.

There are newly added special stages, which truly surprised me the most, at first I had no clue what those diamonds were from a couple of hidden blocks, came unexpected.

Played this out with random characters, and the ending though was something lol.

#SonicFanGames #SonicBoll
Link is here!
By Team Boll:
https://sonicminusworld.wordpress.com/
